sk for information. No information is better then wrong one taken as true","line":9},{"title":"Begin by making them say “No”.","target":"Begin by making them say “No”.","line":10},{"title":"Beware that, when fighting monsters, you yourself do not become a monster... for when you gaze long into the abyss. The abyss gazes also into you","target":"Beware that, when fighting monsters, you yourself do not become a monster... for when you gaze long into the abyss. The abyss gazes also into you","line":11},{"title":"C sharp programování","target":"C sharp programování","line":12},{"title":"Catastrophe you expect to happen already happened","target":"Catastrophe you expect to happen already happened","line":13},{"title":"Chatgpt generation of questions for game - generate 20 questions","target":"Chatgpt generation of questions for game - generate 20 questions","line":14},{"title":"Christina Things to encourage","target":"Christina Things to encourage","line":15},{"title":"cleaning","target":"cleaning","line":16},{"title":"Co mám říct aby mě nechal napokoji Máš pravdu","target":"Co mám říct aby mě nechal napokoji Máš pravdu","line":17},{"title":"Co nejhoršího se může stát🦴","target":"Co nejhoršího se může stát🦴","line":18},{"title":"Compassion as “a sensitivity to the suffering of others, with a commitment to do something about it,” -Dalai Lama","target":"Compassion as “a sensitivity to the suffering of others, with a commitment to do something about it,” -Dalai Lama","line":19},{"title":"Criticism as Feedback- What need is not being met","target":"Criticism as Feedback- What need is not being met","line":20},{"title":"Dashboard","target":"Dashboard","line":21},{"title":"ddgg","target":"ddgg","line":22},{"title":"diffuse-mode activators","target":"diffuse-mode activators","line":23},{"title":"Digital garden inspirace","target":"Digital garden inspirace","line":24},{"title":"Don't aim at success-the more you aim at it and make it a target, the more you are going to miss it.","target":"Don't aim at success-the more you aim at it and make it a target, the more you are going to miss it.","line":25},{"title":"Don't let emotion to control you, but use it as information about present environment.","target":"Don't let emotion to control you, but use it as information about present environment.","line":26},{"title":"Don't rely on chance of enemy not attacking, but rather on the fact that we have made our position unassailable.”","target":"Don't rely on chance of enemy not attacking, but rather on the fact that we have made our position unassailable.”","line":27},{"title":"drafts tips","target":"drafts tips","line":28},{"title":"Energické rytmy těla v průběhu dne","target":"Energické rytmy těla v průběhu dne","line":29},{"title":"Every time you do something that is one less time you do it.","target":"Every time you do something that is one less time you do it.","line":30},{"title":"Good life algorithm","target":"Good life algorithm","line":31},{"title":"Highlights to obsidian","target":"Highlights to obsidian","line":32},{"title":"How much I would bet it to be true","target":"How much I would bet it to be true","line":33},{"title":"How to take better notes","target":"How to take better notes","line":34},{"title":"How To turn someone from rude into respectfull","target":"How To turn someone from rude into respectfull","line":35},{"title":"I am not really happy with obsidian sync. Is there a better option (for iOS)  rObsidianMD","target":"I am not really happy with obsidian sync. Is there a better option (for iOS)  rObsidianMD","line":36},{"title":"If everything is valuable then everything has equal value. And that equal value is zero.","target":"If everything is valuable then everything has equal value. And that equal value is zero.","line":37},{"title":"If you are reading this, you have survived your entire life up until this point.","target":"If you are reading this, you have survived your entire life up until this point.","line":38},{"title":"If you think Christianity is hard you will not succeed. If you think it's impossible you might succeed.","target":"If you think Christianity is hard you will not succeed. If you think it's impossible you might succeed.","line":39},{"title":"IMG-20250331134441008.png","target":"IMG-20250331134441008.png","line":40},{"title":"Improve focus by train time without blinking","target":"Improve focus by train time without blinking","line":41},{"title":"Jak získat motivaci infografika","target":"Jak získat motivaci infografika","line":42},{"title":"kánon","target":"kánon","line":43},{"title":"Leverage Dopamine To Overcome Procrastination & Optimize Effort - Huberman Lab • Podcast Notes","target":"Leverage Dopamine To Overcome Procrastination & Optimize Effort - Huberman Lab • Podcast Notes","line":44},{"title":"Make the thing you wish you had found when you were learning","target":"Make the thing you wish you had found when you were learning","line":45},{"title":"Make your habits fun","target":"Make your habits fun","line":46},{"title":"Mentoring","target":"Mentoring","line":47},{"title":"MIQ process - Most Important Question","target":"MIQ process - Most Important Question","line":48},{"title":"More time you have less time you have.","target":"More time you have less time you have.","line":49},{"title":"my limiting mindset - challenge it - what I do counter it.","target":"my limiting mindset - challenge it - what I do counter it.","line":50},{"title":"Nejmenší krok ve správném směru","target":"Nejmenší krok ve správném směru","line":51},{"title":"Nobody cares.","target":"Nobody cares.","line":52},{"title":"Nothing is lost, nothing is created, everything is transformed.”","target":"Nothing is lost, nothing is created, everything is transformed.”","line":53},{"title":"Před usnutím si představit","target":"Před usnutím si představit","line":54},{"title":"Raise your ambitions. Lower your expectations.^7e2a87","target":"Raise your ambitions. Lower your expectations.^7e2a87","line":55},{"title":"Řeč těla - moje poznámky","target":"Řeč těla - moje poznámky","line":56},{"title":"Shadow casted by our dream is adequate to size of the dream","target":"Shadow casted by our dream is adequate to size of the dream","line":57},{"title":"Some things won't get easier you only get better at handling them.","target":"Some things won't get easier you only get better at handling them.","line":58},{"title":"Sometimes it’s not about being equipped just about being at the right place at right time","target":"Sometimes it’s not about being equipped just about being at the right place at right time","line":59},{"title":"spinning plates","target":"spinning plates","line":60},{"title":"Start with ice-cream instead of the frog","target":"Start with ice-cream instead of the frog","line":61},{"title":"summarize.tech AI-powered video summaries","target":"summarize.tech AI-powered video summaries","line":62},{"title":"Test 2","target":"Test 2","line":63},{"title":"Test","target":"Test","line":64},{"title":"test","target":"test","line":65},{"title":"thaibox notes","target":"thaibox notes","line":66},{"title":"The best ideas often comes from bad ideas -- don't be afraid to think about all- bad and good ideas","target":"The best ideas often comes from bad ideas -- don't be afraid to think about all- bad and good ideas","line":67},{"title":"The concept of “mental health” in our society is defined largely by the extent to which an individual behaves in accord with the needs of the system and does so without showing signs of stress.” -Theodor Unabomber Kaczynski","target":"The concept of “mental health” in our society is defined largely by the extent to which an individual behaves in accord with the needs of the system and does so without showing signs of stress.” -Theodor Unabomber Kaczynski","line":68},{"title":"The permanent Benefits of a 15 Minute Meditation Practice","target":"The permanent Benefits of a 15 Minute Meditation Practice","line":69},{"title":"To make a room luxurious, remove things, rather than add things.","target":"To make a room luxurious, remove things, rather than add things.","line":70},{"title":"Untitled 2","target":"Untitled 2","line":71},{"title":"Untitled 3","target":"Untitled 3","line":72},{"title":"Untitled 4","target":"Untitled 4","line":73},{"title":"Untitled 5","target":"Untitled 5","line":74},{"title":"Untitled 6","target":"Untitled 6","line":75},{"title":"Untitled 8","target":"Untitled 8","line":76},{"title":"Untitled 9","target":"Untitled 9","line":77},{"title":"Untitled 11","target":"Untitled 11","line":78},{"title":"Untitled 12","target":"Untitled 12","line":79},{"title":"🕸️Network map","target":"🕸️Network map","line":80},{"title":"Victim vs Survivor","target":"Victim vs Survivor","line":81},{"title":"Visual focus is followed by cognitive focus","target":"Visual focus is followed by cognitive focus","line":82},{"title":"What is the worst day and what is the best day","target":"What is the worst day and what is the best day","line":83},{"title":"When a child asks an endless string of “why” questions, the smartest reply is, “I don’t know, what do you think”","target":"When a child asks an endless string of “why” questions, the smartest reply is, “I don’t know, what do you think”","line":84},{"title":"When a person can’t find a deep sense of meaning, they distract themselves with pleasure.” – Viktor Frankl","target":"When a person can’t find a deep sense of meaning, they distract themselves with pleasure.” – Viktor Frankl","line":85},{"title":"When getting rid of unwanted stuff we need to supplement it with something else or it will bounce back worse","target":"When getting rid of unwanted stuff we need to supplement it with something else or it will bounce back worse","line":86},{"title":"Where is next 1% I could improve","target":"Where is next 1% I could improve","line":87},{"title":"Will I do the thing or suffer the rest of the life","target":"Will I do the thing or suffer the rest of the life","line":88},{"title":"willpower","target":"willpower","line":89},{"title":"You can't do everything, but you can do one thing, and then another and another.","target":"You can't do everything, but you can do one thing, and then another and another.","line":90},{"title":"Your best response to an insult is “You’re probably right.” Often they are","target":"Your best response to an insult is “You’re probably right.” Often they are","line":91},{"title":"Your life is designed to get the results you are getting right now. For the trajectory to change, the approach must change.","target":"Your life is designed to get the results you are getting right now. For the trajectory to change, the approach must change.","line":92},{"title":"Your true values show up in two places - your calendar and your bank account.","target":"Your true values show up in two places - your calendar and your bank account.","line":93}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"tczent","at":1772113994082}},
